From our very first trial podcast for @aesthe.ticks 🎬 // No one tells you how much goes into creating something from scratch. The energy, the self-doubt, the fight to make it exactly how you imagined. 

It’s about believing in something before the world sees it. About putting in the work, the late nights, the doubts, and still showing up.

Trust me, it takes time, effort, courage & a whole lot of heart to bring an idea to life and make it actually good.

And here we are, making it happen. With heart, with passion, with no looking back. 
Building @aesthe.ticks with @chaitali.thakker has been a ride—one that’s just getting started.  #latepost

📰This Women’s Day, we’re proud to share a video we created for @trysugar ‘s campaign—celebrating fearless women who dared to carve their own path. ✨

This journey of standing by our vision and making bold choices has not only helped us build Aestheticks but has also shaped us into who we are today, teaching us invaluable lessons along the way. Every challenge, every decision, and every “no” has played a part in our growth. 🌻

Wishing all the incredible women in our lives a Happy Women’s Day! Here’s to strength, resilience, and making an impact, no matter how big or small. 🎀
